OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FFresh west to northwest winds
OL,6,Fbringing showers across the area
OL,7,Ftoday. Outbreaks ranging from frequent
OL,8,Fin Argyll, and scattered elsewhere
OL,9,Fwith the best of the limited brighter
OL,10,Fspells appearing in the Central Belt.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA rather cloudy evening with
OL,13,Ffurther showers, these focused across
OL,14,FArgyll. Clear spells developing
OL,15,Fovernight, particularly from the
OL,16,FCentral Belt southwards where showers
OL,17,Fdie out.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
